Onboarding Dumitru Zavrotschi as the facilitator of the TechOps Core Unit.

## Specification

### Motivation

I am happy that the Maker Foundation reached its goals and dissolved, making the way to the creation of a real DAO with multiple core units responsible for ecosystem. My wish is to contribute to Maker Protocol stability, quality, growth and expansion. I believe that my skills and experience, together with the years spent as a Maker Foundation team member, make me a good candidate for TechOps Core Unit Facilitator role, where TechOps Core Unit is serving the Protocol by keeping secure, reliable and transparent infrastructure.

### Core Unit Name

TechOps Core Unit

