### Facilitator Commitment

My role will be in commitment to keep TechOps Core Unit running smoothly and the daily tasks may include:
- Be the Facilitator and Quality Assurance Lead for TechOps Core Unit
- Be the main contact person for TechOps Core Unit
- Support the community by providing and executing various technical tasks
- Communicate Core Unit work progress and results
- Maintain transparency in work, tasks and any updates done by and within the Core Unit
- Contribute to further Core Unit growth, process improvements and staying up-to-date with the latest tech trends

